column16: Albert Pujols homers (5) on a line drive to left field.   Collin Cowgill scores.    Mike Trout scores.
Collin Cowgill doubles (2) on a line drive to left fielder Rajai Davis.
Ian Stewart pops out to third baseman Don Kelly.
John McDonald pops out to shortstop Andrew Romine.
J.  B.   Shuck grounds out sharply, first baseman Miguel Cabrera to pitcher Luke Putkonen.
Umpire reviewed (home run), call on the field was overturned: Howie Kendrick homers (2) on a line drive to right center field.    Mike Trout scores.
Albert Pujols grounds out, third baseman Don Kelly to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
Mike Trout doubles (6) on a line drive to left fielder Rajai Davis.   Ian Stewart scores.    Collin Cowgill scores.
Ian Stewart doubles (2) on a line drive to right fielder Torii Hunter.
John McDonald grounds out, third baseman Don Kelly to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
Jedd Gyorko lines out softly to shortstop Andrew Romine.
Seth Smith grounds into a force out, first baseman Victor Martinez to shortstop Andrew Romine.   Everth Cabrera scores.    Chris Denorfia out at 2nd.    Seth Smith to 1st.
Chris Denorfia reaches on a fielder's choice, fielded by shortstop Andrew Romine.   Andrew Cashner scores.    Everth Cabrera to 3rd.
Everth Cabrera singles on a ground ball to right fielder Don Kelly, deflected by second baseman Ian Kinsler.   Andrew Cashner to 3rd.
